<section>
  <h2>What FISCO does</h2>
  <p>FISCO operationalises the EU's reformed economic governance framework for IFIs. It assesses both the design of the medium-term plan and its annual implementation against the net-expenditure rule, the debt and deficit benchmarks, and the operation of the control account.</p>

  <div class="card-grid">
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Plan assessment</h3>
      <p>Tests the recommended net-expenditure path against debt sustainability, deficit, and minimum-effort safeguards, with full visibility of the underlying calculations.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Implementation monitoring</h3>
      <p>Tracks annual deviations and the cumulative control account, and surfaces breaches of the 0.3% and 0.6% of GDP thresholds.</p>
    </article>
    <article class="card">
      <h3>Built for IFIs</h3>
      <p>Transparent formulas, sourceable data (Eurostat + AMECO), and a step-by-step workflow with embedded video tutorials.</p>
    </article>
  </div>
</section>
